Barcelona won the treble in 2009 . 
  Eric Abidal says his former club can win La Liga, the Champions League and the Copa del Rey this season . 
  Barcelona beat Paris Saint-Germain 2-0 to advance to the semi-finals of the UEFA Champions League . 
  Abidal was part of the team that won six trophies in 2009 and says the current crop are on their way . 
 